Welcome to ChaldOS — Pixel Operating System
=============================================

ChaldOS is a lightweight Linux distribution focused on
simplicity, pixel-perfect aesthetics, and modern hardware support.

Boot options:
  ChaldOS              — Normal boot (recommended)
  ChaldOS Safe Mode    — Boot without graphics acceleration
  ChaldOS Debug        — Boot with verbose kernel messages
  ChaldOS Live (RAM)   — Boot into memory (live session)
  Memory Test          — Run memtest86
  Boot from Local Drive — Boot installed OS

Press ENTER to boot, or TAB to edit boot parameters.
